<div class="story">
<p>Heron Cove condos are located on the oceanfront in Nags Head  directly across the street from the <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/nags head/coastal-cove.asp" title="Coastal Cove">Coastal Cove</a> subdivision and just north of <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/nags head/admirals-view.asp" title="Admirals View Condos">Admirals View Condos</a>. There are 2 buildings next to each other and each building has an elevator for all of the units to share. Each condo is roughly 2,000 sq ft and have 3 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms. The penthouse units offer panoramic ocean views, the second floor units have good ocean views and the first floor units have a view of the ocean front dune with a little bit of ocean view peeking over the low spots in the dune. Covered parking and a community ocean front pool round off the amenities. </p>
